data.description: Property will be available for showings on Saturday 11/18.  Outstanding home in Hidden Pond. This full brick front 4-bedroom 2.5 bath home has so much to bring to the table.  Enter into a 2-story foyer and new laminate throughout the first floor.  There is a formal living room and dining room with crown and chair rail molding and a double side staircase to the second floor. The eat in kitchen has tons of cabinet and counter space as well as a center island. A full pantry gives even more storage for the chef.  A gas stove, recessed lighting and tile backsplash enhance this kitchen even more. The family room off the kitchen makes gatherings a come together event.  A private office/den on the first floor too, for a little privacy when you need it.  Upstairs are 4 great-sized bedrooms. The main bedroom offers a huge sitting area, three closets and trey ceiling and adjoining bath has dual vanities, soaking tub and a 4-foot tile shower.  Cap all this home has to offer off with a full basement ready to be finished, a massive three car garage and a patio out back to sit back on and relax an evening away.  This home is in move in condition. Recently painted and well maintained. Make your appointment today!
